channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://i62.tinypic.com/24ky1ow.jpg[/img][/center]
[center]Hello, My name is Ryan and i have recently started getting back into owning/coding rsps. I have been working on this server over the years, and now want to perfect it. I am looking for a dedicated team to help me along the way, and to make Element grow. As you can see from the picture above I'm not the best gfx artist, so i will be needing one. I will also need a developer both client sided and server sided to help with things. I can make an OK website, but I'm looking for a Web Developer, who knows more and who can watch over site.[/center]
[u][center]People On Team Element[/center][/u] [center]Justin (advertiser)[/center]
[u][center]People I Need[/center][/u] [center]Coders (client/server) Gfx Artist Web Developer [/center] [center]Information[/center] [center]Bought a domain Paying for Website, when i find Web Developer Paying for VPS, when server is ready [/center] Pictures:
